      <title>英国 TSB 银行因不公平对待客户被罚款</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/britains-tsb-bank-fined-unfair-treatment-customers-2024-10-10/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[市场监管机构周四表示，英国 TSB 银行因未能确保拖欠款项的客户得到公平对待，被罚款 1090 万英镑（1425 万美元）。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/britains-tsb-bank-fined-unfair-treatment-customers-2024-10-10/</guid>
